	&lt;li&gt;According to the context of the given sentence, &lt;strong&gt;Marie &lt;/strong&gt;asked the &lt;strong&gt;subject &lt;/strong&gt;to wait for a &lt;strong&gt;short while.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
