	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li role=&quot;presentation&quot;&gt;Among the options, the phrase that matches this meaning is &amp;#39;To wait quietly for a good opportunity to do something&amp;#39;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Therefore, the correct answer is Option 4.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;The &lt;strong&gt;correct answer &lt;/strong&gt;is &lt;strong&gt;option 3 &lt;/strong&gt;i.e. &amp;#39;&lt;strong&gt;Tuition&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;#39;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

