	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;On cloud nine &lt;/strong&gt;(&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;बहुत खुश&lt;/span&gt;): To be extremely happy.
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Example:&lt;/strong&gt; She was on cloud nine after winning the competition.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
