&lt;p&gt;S: Hobby is a leisure time activity.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;R: Whatever leisure time you get, you use that in creative activity.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Q: In due course, that becomes your hobby.&lt;/p&gt;

